name: Psycho Log
description:
Exact your revenge on the pesky beavers that have invaded your forest and used your fellow logs in their dams!

Pscycho Log is an endless floater about one log, thicker and gnarlier than the rest of them. Ram as many beavers as you can, and avoid obstacles to build up speed, so you can take out the beaver dams and free your brethren!

  • natural splendor all around you
  • many wet beavers to ram with your thick log
  • three hoofin' bluegrass tune by The Possum Whackers



THIS GAME ONLY RUNS IN THE BROWSER
